<div class='panel'><h2>rules</h2>

<p>generally, don't be a bad person.</h2>

<ul>
  <li>corporate accounts are cool, but please limit public posts</li>
  <li>parodies are fine if they are obvious, but including that it is a parody somewhere in the profile would be best</li>
  <li>bots are not allowed to post to the public timeline without permission from an admin and may not interact with users without direct user permission</li>
  <li>content that is illegal anywhere in the United States or Canada is a bannable offence without appeal</li>
  <li>hate speech or similar is forbidden</li>
</ul>

<p>rules may change at any time and ultimately, everything is left up to the discretion of the administration.</p>

<p>currently, <a href="https://hex.bz/@fox">fox@hex.bz</a> is the only admin. please contact them if you have any issues.</p></div>
